result.name: Ole Spanish Restaurant

reviews.text: The atmosphere was intimate and cozy, the staff was very kind, nice and helpful, and the food was delicious! Truly Spanish dishes and flavours. The two guitarists/singers were very talented and played beautifully.
"One of the best Spanish restaurant in HK. " was the comment from my Spanish friend. That said it all! They have live guitar music on Sunday brunch and dinner. Shouldn't miss that out!
Elegant dining atmosphere. Food, exceptional. I'm already ready to go back for the things I didn't eat but saw and smelled pass by.

Poor poor service... I called to make reservation for four and was told they are full for 12pm but can come at 12.15pm (whole 15 mins difference).

I arrived to see a 20% occupied restaurant and it's now 1pm and it's around 60% full.  To cap off matters, the waitresses are definitely not interested to serve their guests.

For instance, when we finished the soup, she only took the bowl and left the plate as if she was too lazy to come back with a clean plate.

What happened?!?  We came here for lunch because my wife likes it and my gals are on holiday... I much prefer to go to Wolfgang

Hkd210 lunch set - goat cheese salad+fisherman seafood+fried milk+coffee. Enjoy the hospitality of papa owner who came chatting with us.
Sat brunch is not bad at hkd470 per person. The suckling Pig is too gamey. Deep fried milk didn’t taste as gd as last time.

result.name: Ole Spanish Restaurant

reviews.text: The atmosphere was intimate and cozy, the staff was very kind, nice and helpful, and the food was delicious! Truly Spanish dishes and flavours. The two guitarists/singers were very talented and played beautifully.

歷久不衰的好味道。
三道菜式的午間套餐HKD250有找。
前菜不論選沙拉或是湯都不會失望。
主菜選擇很多，想好自己偏好，魚，肉，或是西班牙式料理，可以幫助快速决定。
餐後甜點提拉米蘇或是冰淇淋都很美味，咖啡就用來解膩而非品嚐。
"One of the best Spanish restaurant in HK. " was the comment from my Spanish friend. That said it all! They have live guitar music on Sunday brunch and dinner. Shouldn't miss that out!
Elegant dining atmosphere. Food, exceptional. I'm already ready to go back for the things I didn't eat but saw and smelled pass by.
餐廳非常有氣氛，佈置如親臨西班牙一樣，美食水準高，精緻同時能飽腹，不妨再加上著名的利口酒及雪梨酒。但建議二人同行及先行預約。
